---
title: Thai Pork Laarb Burger Cucumber-Mint Salad
description: Laarb is a traditional Northern Thai dish composed of stir-fried ground meats, chilies, herbs, and pungent spices. This dish transforms those same flavors into a juicy burger that’s spiked with fragrant lemongrass, shallot, mint, and garlic. Offset by a crisp cucumber-mint salad, this dinner brings you the complex flavors of Northern Thailand in a simple, 35 minute recipe.
